## Testing Strategy

### Cross-validation with read_pgen

Test data was generated from VCF → pgen via plink2. So:
```sql
SELECT * FROM read_vcf('test/data/example.vcf') ORDER BY POS
-- must match --
SELECT * FROM read_pgen('test/data/pgen_example.pgen') ORDER BY POS
```

### Test cases

- Row count, column types, genotype values
- .vcf vs .vcf.gz produce identical results
- Parameters: samples, region, orient, genotypes, phased
- Negative: missing file, no #CHROM header, no GT field, empty file
- Edge cases: multi-allelic, missing genotypes, half-calls

