## Risks

| Risk | Mitigation |
|------|------------|
| Extraction script fragile (function boundaries shift) | Grep by function name, not line number. VCF format stable. |
| textFILE uses FILE* (no S3/HTTP) | Document local-only for Phase 1. DuckDB VFS fallback later. |
| Extracted parsers depend on plink2_base.h internals | Already compiled; pin submodule = pin ABI. |
| Platform issues with textFILE | Already compiled on all platforms in pgenlib. |
| BCF not covered in Phase 1 | Separate parser extraction; BCF is Phase 2. |

